[SPEAKER_01] Nisi znao da ću umrijeti.

840
00:26:38,480 --> 00:26:44,279
[SPEAKER_01] I on dan, pazite sad ovo, izrade smrtovnicu,

841
00:26:44,279 --> 00:26:47,779
[SPEAKER_01] čak uplate u večernjaku Slobodna Dalmacija,

842
00:26:47,779 --> 00:26:50,700
[SPEAKER_01] jutarnji, ono na zadnje par stranica one oglase

843
00:26:50,700 --> 00:26:55,940
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže, u dubokoj tuzi javljamo iznenada je umro.

844
00:26:56,359 --> 00:26:58,799
[SPEAKER_01] I tamo vidiš 95 godina, jel?

845
00:26:58,799 --> 00:27:02,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ja rekao, gospođo draga, bolje da upišete u novima

846
00:27:02,400 --> 00:27:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] iznenada se oženio za sina ili iznenada diplomiro.

847
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:08,680
[SPEAKER_01] To je meni puno veće.

848
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:11,539
[SPEAKER_01] Nije smrti iznenađenje.

849
00:27:11,539 --> 00:27:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedino što ja znam da će se dogoditi.

850
00:27:14,599 --> 00:27:19,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedine što ja znam da će se meni dogoditi.

851
00:27:19,000 --> 00:27:20,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ja ću umrijeti.

852
00:27:20,359 --> 00:27:21,799
[SPEAKER_01] Umrijet ću.

853
00:27:21,799 --> 00:27:26,099
[SPEAKER_01] I kako se suočavamo s time?

854
00:27:26,359 --> 00:27:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se s time suočavamo?

855
00:27:29,119 --> 00:27:36,319
[SPEAKER_01] Jer vi znate da je to najvažniji trenutak tvog života.

856
00:27:36,319 --> 00:27:37,200
[SPEAKER_01] Znate zašto?

857
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] Jer u tom trenutku odlučuješ cijelu vječnost.

858
00:27:41,480 --> 00:27:42,700
[SPEAKER_01] Sami ste vi to?

859
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:49,119
[SPEAKER_01] Da u tom trenutku ti možeš zapravo odlučit se.

860
00:27:49,119 --> 00:27:51,299
[SPEAKER_01] To je na radnik 11. ure.

861
00:27:51,299 --> 00:27:57,720
[SPEAKER_01] Cijelu svoja, cijela tvoja vječnost visi o tom trenutku.

862
00:27:57,720 --> 00:28:02,980
[SPEAKER_01] Zato molimo u zdravo Marije sada i na času smrti.

863
00:28:02,980 --> 00:28:03,299
[SPEAKER_01] Amen.

864
00:28:03,299 --> 00:28:05,900
[SPEAKER_01] Zapravo dva su najvažnija trenutaka života.

865
00:28:05,900 --> 00:28:06,400
[SPEAKER_01] Znate koja?

866
00:28:06,400 --> 00:28:08,039
[SPEAKER_01] Sada i smrt.

867
00:28:08,039 --> 00:28:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Budući da sada se odmah pretvaraju u nova sad jer vrijeme ide.

868
00:28:11,500 --> 00:28:12,759
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki trenutak je važan.

869
00:28:12,759 --> 00:28:16,079
[SPEAKER_01] To je dosta zgodno rečeno u zdravo Marije.

870
00:28:16,079 --> 00:28:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] Sada i na času smrti.

871
00:28:17,559 --> 00:28:21,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ja želim u času smrti biti spreman.

872
00:28:21,099 --> 00:28:24,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja želim ne bježati.

873
00:28:24,420 --> 00:28:26,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ja želim se s tim suočiti i biti spreman.

874
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:34,460
[SPEAKER_01] Zato crkva, majka crkva, koja želi biti svojom djecom u svakoj fazi života.

875
00:28:34,460 --> 00:28:37,779
[SPEAKER_01] Zato od rođenja, majka crkva želi tu pa te krstimo.

876
00:28:37,779 --> 00:28:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] U odrastanju mi želimo tu biti, zato te hranimo Ehoristijom.

877
00:28:41,900 --> 00:28:44,099
[SPEAKER_01] Zato te saljamo u krizmi, da te osnažimo.

878
00:28:44,099 --> 00:28:45,259
[SPEAKER_01] Zato te ženimo.

879
00:28:45,259 --> 00:28:49,799
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, ko svaki roditelj, ti želiš biti s tvojim djetetom u svakom trenutku.

880
00:28:49,799 --> 00:28:53,359
[SPEAKER_01] I u trenutku kad su zločestni moraš ih disciplinirati.

881
00:28:53,359 --> 00:28:54,359
[SPEAKER_01] Zato imamo ispovjed.

882
00:28:54,359 --> 00:28:59,980
[SPEAKER_01] I tako majka crkva želi biti sa svojom djecom kad ona umre.

883
00:28:59,980 --> 00:29:01,200
[SPEAKER_01] Kad ona umire.

884
00:29:01,200 --> 00:29:03,740
[SPEAKER_01] I zato imamo ovaj sakravenat.

885
00:29:03,740 --> 00:29:09,559
[SPEAKER_01] Kao što sam već spomenio, to je Isus Krist ustanovio.

886
00:29:10,559 --> 00:29:15,319
[SPEAKER_01] I što se tiče naziva, ono se prije zvalo posljedna pomast,

887
00:29:15,319 --> 00:29:18,859
[SPEAKER_01] ali u novije vrijeme, Bogu hvala, ono se zove bolestiško pomazanje.

888
00:29:18,859 --> 00:29:20,519
[SPEAKER_01] I Bogu hvala na tome.

889
00:29:20,519 --> 00:29:21,140
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto?

890
00:29:21,140 --> 00:29:23,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ima ljudi u našim selima.

891
00:29:23,460 --> 00:29:29,299
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam, evo, to je iz razloga zašto prosječan Hrvat neće zvati svećenika.

892
00:29:29,299 --> 00:29:32,240
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što kad vide svećenika, gotovo je smrt.

893
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] To je to, on nosi smrt.

894
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,619
[SPEAKER_01] Pa je, pa ja.

895
00:29:36,619 --> 00:29:38,940
[SPEAKER_01] I zato taj izraz mi nije dobar.

896
00:29:38,940 --> 00:29:39,980
[SPEAKER_01] Posljedna pomast.

897
00:29:39,980 --> 00:29:41,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, bolestiško pomazanje.

898
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:42,759
[SPEAKER_01] Si bolestan?

899
00:29:42,759 --> 00:29:43,240
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi.

900
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:44,980
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja sam tu za tebe.

901
00:29:44,980 --> 00:29:51,240
[SPEAKER_01] Zato neki kažu, ja mislim kad već požuti, kad mu ust ne drte,

902
00:29:51,240 --> 00:29:53,460
[SPEAKER_01] evo sad ćemo svećenika zvati.

903
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:56,759
[SPEAKER_01] Krivo, krivo, krivo.

904
00:29:56,759 --> 00:29:58,019
[SPEAKER_01] Okej, nemojte to.

905
00:29:58,019 --> 00:30:01,759
[SPEAKER_01] Pogotovo vi koji imate nekoga doma ili koji ste bolestni.

906
00:30:01,759 --> 00:30:05,039
[SPEAKER_01] Što mene tiče, svi koji preko 65 godina su kandidati.

907
00:30:05,039 --> 00:30:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] Kakvi? Svi preko 60 su kandidati.

908
00:30:08,380 --> 00:30:09,859
[SPEAKER_01] Okej.

909
00:30:09,859 --> 00:30:15,059
[SPEAKER_01] E, slušajte ovo.

910
00:30:15,059 --> 00:30:16,099
[SPEAKER_01] Pazite sad ovo.

911
00:30:16,099 --> 00:30:19,680
[SPEAKER_01] Tko smije primati bolestiško pomazanje?

912
00:30:20,900 --> 00:30:25,839
[SPEAKER_01] Znate, crkva je vrlo, kad piše dokumenta, ona je sjednostavno vrlo općenita.

913
00:30:25,839 --> 00:30:29,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ona sve kaže, ali i neke ljudima to ide na živce.

914
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:33,700
[SPEAKER_01] A to je što točno ne opisuje detalje.

915
00:30:33,700 --> 00:30:37,960
[SPEAKER_01] Naprimjer, ja ne znam, jel vi očekujete dva tkana, neka mora biti treći stadiju, rak.

916
00:30:37,960 --> 00:30:41,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ne znam šta očekujete, ali ovo su kriteriji.

917
00:30:41,880 --> 00:30:42,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže ovako.

918
00:30:42,519 --> 00:30:48,259
[SPEAKER_01] Zbog bolesti ili starosti koji se nalazi na početku smrtne pogeblje.

919
00:30:49,880 --> 00:30:52,839
[SPEAKER_01] I kao što vidite, to se može tumačiti kako hoćeš, jel?

920
00:30:52,839 --> 00:30:58,759
[SPEAKER_01] Ali meni je drago što naša crkva ne ide u takve detalje, da je apsolutno sve definirano.

921
00:30:58,759 --> 00:31:00,380
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje se daje jedna sloboda.

922
00:31:00,380 --> 00:31:06,440
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, ovaj se sakrament može ponoviti ako bolestnik po primljenoj pomasti prizdravi,

923
00:31:06,440 --> 00:31:08,339
[SPEAKER_01] a onda nastupi druga teška bolest.

924
00:31:08,339 --> 00:31:10,319
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sakrament se može ponoviti.

925
00:31:11,220 --> 00:31:17,680
[SPEAKER_01] Također ovdje kaže, u tijeku iste bolici sakrament se može ponoviti ako nastupi pogoršenje.

926
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:24,119
[SPEAKER_01] Čak ovdje kaže, prije kiruškog zahvata. Čak to piše u dokumentu.

927
00:31:24,119 --> 00:31:26,359
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da je to jedan napredak.

928
00:31:27,359 --> 00:31:31,940
[SPEAKER_01] I Bogu fala, ljudi kažu, velčastinu operaciju i tako dalje.

929
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:32,940
[SPEAKER_01] I to je okej.

930
00:31:32,940 --> 00:31:40,099
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže, isto vrijedi i za starije osobe kojih nemoć biva sve veća.

931
00:31:40,099 --> 00:31:42,420
[SPEAKER_01] Sad, ko ima uši, neka čuje.

932
00:31:42,420 --> 00:31:50,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kada sam ja kao svećenik odbio bolestčko pomazanje,

933
00:31:50,000 --> 00:31:52,660
[SPEAKER_01] najgore mi je kad mi dođe trudnica.

934
00:31:52,660 --> 00:31:56,119
[SPEAKER_01] I kaže, draga moja, ko ti je rekao da je trudnoća bolest?

935
00:31:56,380 --> 00:32:00,259
[SPEAKER_01] To ne. Neko dođe, ima migrenu, glavobolju.

936
00:32:00,259 --> 00:32:04,240
[SPEAKER_01] Ona je, malo pitaš, nije spavao sinoć jer je bančio van

937
00:32:04,240 --> 00:32:06,359
[SPEAKER_01] i sad ga glava boli, traži blešku pomazanje.

938
00:32:06,359 --> 00:32:07,980
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, draga, aj ti spava i pi vodu.

939
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:15,539
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, obično ja sam, vidite, upoznam svećenike koji dijele šakom i kapom.

940
00:32:15,539 --> 00:32:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam protiv toga.

941
00:32:17,000 --> 00:32:21,119
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam malo, malo tu konzervativni.

942
00:32:21,119 --> 00:32:24,839
[SPEAKER_01] Ja mislim da to bi trebao biti osoba koja je starija,

943
00:32:25,019 --> 00:32:28,140
[SPEAKER_01] koja već malo pomalo se gasi, slabiji u tijelu,

944
00:32:28,140 --> 00:32:31,440
[SPEAKER_01] koji ide na kiruški zakvat i koji ima ozbilnu dijagnozu.

945
00:32:31,440 --> 00:32:34,500
[SPEAKER_01] Oni su za bolestičko pomazanje.

946
00:32:36,359 --> 00:32:39,859
[SPEAKER_01] Još jedna sitnica, samo svećenici i biskupi smije.

947
00:32:39,859 --> 00:32:42,859
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, džako ne lajkne, samo svećenik i biskupi.

948
00:32:42,859 --> 00:32:45,220
[SPEAKER_01] I to dolazimo od Jakovljave poznanice.

949
00:32:45,220 --> 00:32:48,059
[SPEAKER_01] I također Marko 6 gdje Isus ne šalja svakoga,

950
00:32:48,059 --> 00:32:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] njegove apostole.

951
00:32:49,539 --> 00:32:52,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, na temelju toga crkva smatra,

952
00:32:53,779 --> 00:32:56,059
[SPEAKER_01] i vjeruje i drži od početka,

953
00:32:56,059 --> 00:33:00,420
[SPEAKER_01] da samo svećenik i da samo biskup može to dijeliti.

954
00:33:00,420 --> 00:33:01,500
[SPEAKER_01] Onaj koji ima sveti red.

955
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,779
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, kako to slavlje izgleda?

956
00:33:03,779 --> 00:33:07,539
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja sam čak donio obrednik bleškog pomazanja

957
00:33:07,539 --> 00:33:11,160
[SPEAKER_01] i ja ću to malo s vama proć.

958
00:33:11,160 --> 00:33:15,680
[SPEAKER_01] I zanimljivo, počinje sa škropljenjem vode.

959
00:33:15,680 --> 00:33:17,779
[SPEAKER_01] Jako zanimljivo.

960
00:33:17,779 --> 00:33:18,779
[SPEAKER_01] Znate zašto?

961
00:33:18,779 --> 00:33:22,460
[SPEAKER_01] Zato što prvi put kad si ti poškropljen vodom

962
00:33:22,460 --> 00:33:24,200
[SPEAKER_01] je bilo krštenje.

963
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:27,700
[SPEAKER_01] A na dan krštenja ti si umro samom sebi.

964
00:33:27,700 --> 00:33:32,500
[SPEAKER_01] Nasupra što ljudi misle,

965
00:33:32,500 --> 00:33:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] krštenje je sakrmenat križa.

966
00:33:35,079 --> 00:33:36,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mnogi ljudi to ne povezuju, ali jest.

967
00:33:36,880 --> 00:33:39,579
[SPEAKER_01] Isus se kaže da se ima krsti s svojim krstom

968
00:33:39,579 --> 00:33:41,039
[SPEAKER_01] i omizi na smrt svoju.

969
00:33:41,039 --> 00:33:45,940
[SPEAKER_01] I zato ono uranjanje u vodu,

970
00:33:45,940 --> 00:33:47,740
[SPEAKER_01] iako mi škropimo, mi poljevamo,

971
00:33:47,740 --> 00:33:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] ali može se uranjati i izlazi novi čovjek.

972
00:33:50,400 --> 00:33:52,740
[SPEAKER_01] I tako mi je lijepo

973
00:33:52,740 --> 00:33:55,700
[SPEAKER_01] da ovaj sakrmenat počinje

974
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:58,039
[SPEAKER_01] na podsjetnik tvog krštenja.

975
00:33:58,039 --> 00:34:01,000
[SPEAKER_01] Kako počinje obred sprovod,

976
00:34:01,000 --> 00:34:02,680
[SPEAKER_01] to nije sakrmenat, obred sprovod,

977
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] škropimo lije si tijelo.

978
00:34:04,559 --> 00:34:06,839
[SPEAKER_01] Predivno nešto.

979
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:11,440
[SPEAKER_01] To znači uska povezanost između krštenja

980
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:12,599
[SPEAKER_01] i bleško pomazanje.

981
00:34:12,599 --> 00:34:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] Mi prvo te škropimo.

982
00:34:13,699 --> 00:34:14,760
[SPEAKER_01] To je prvo.

983
00:34:16,119 --> 00:34:19,820
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga svećenik ima poticajnu riječ.

984
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:22,860
[SPEAKER_01] Čak ima ovdje jedan predložak,

985
00:34:22,860 --> 00:34:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] kao jedan uvodni nagovor.

986
00:34:24,440 --> 00:34:27,539
[SPEAKER_01] I obično to su riječi utjehe,

987
00:34:27,539 --> 00:34:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] to su riječi poticanje na vjeru,

988
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:32,380
[SPEAKER_01] na nadu, na ufanje i tako dalje.

989
00:34:32,380 --> 00:34:33,579
[SPEAKER_01] Spomenje se ovo Jakova

990
00:34:33,579 --> 00:34:34,940
[SPEAKER_01] i spomenje se da je Isus živ.

991
00:34:35,059 --> 00:34:36,800
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, pobuđujem vjeru.

992
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:40,699
[SPEAKER_01] I svjestan sam da mnogi moji brača svećenici

993
00:34:40,699 --> 00:34:42,059
[SPEAKER_01] malo to ofrljera.

994
00:34:42,059 --> 00:34:43,480
[SPEAKER_01] Ne svi, ali neki da.

995
00:34:43,480 --> 00:34:45,800
[SPEAKER_01] Ali ovo bi trebalo biti slavljeno.

996
00:34:45,800 --> 00:34:48,059
[SPEAKER_01] I predlaže se da bude zajedno u obitelji.

997
00:34:48,059 --> 00:34:49,900
[SPEAKER_01] U zajedništu.

998
00:34:49,900 --> 00:34:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] Predlaže se čak da bude pod misom,

999
00:34:52,019 --> 00:34:52,820
[SPEAKER_01] ako je moguće.

1000
00:34:52,820 --> 00:34:56,300
[SPEAKER_01] Predlaže se da se čovjek ispovidi prije.

1001
00:34:56,780 --> 00:34:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] U slučaju da se neko nije ispovidio,

1002
00:34:58,619 --> 00:35:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] pokajanje za grijehe.

1003
00:35:00,559 --> 00:35:03,300
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon škropljenja vode,

1004
00:35:03,300 --> 00:35:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] nakon podstav vjere,

1005
00:35:04,039 --> 00:35:07,019
[SPEAKER_01] on nam svećenik poziva na kajanje za grijehe.

1006
00:35:07,019 --> 00:35:12,500
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svaka bolest u širem smislu vječi

1007
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:14,820
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi od prvog pada čovjeka.

1008
00:35:14,820 --> 00:35:16,900
[SPEAKER_01] I zato mi se odričimo grijeha.

1009
00:35:16,900 --> 00:35:18,039
[SPEAKER_01] Mi se kajemo za to.

1010
00:35:18,039 --> 00:35:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga slijedi navještaj riječ Božije.

1011
00:35:21,820 --> 00:35:26,019
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, crkva ima prekrasne neke predložke

1012
00:35:26,019 --> 00:35:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] tu iz evanđelje.

1013
00:35:27,380 --> 00:35:29,639
[SPEAKER_01] I onda bi strbalo slijedi podstavne riječi.

1014
00:35:29,639 --> 00:35:30,900
[SPEAKER_01] Opet malo kratka propovjed.

1015
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] Navještaj evanđelje toj osobi.

1016
00:35:32,460 --> 00:35:35,019
[SPEAKER_01] I onda kreće molitva vjernika.

1017
00:35:35,019 --> 00:35:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] Moli se za tog bolesnika.

1018
00:35:36,480 --> 00:35:38,280
[SPEAKER_01] Moli se za oni koji ga dvore.

1019
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:39,440
[SPEAKER_01] Moli se za sve bolesnike.

1020
00:35:39,440 --> 00:35:39,940
[SPEAKER_01] I tako dakle.

1021
00:35:39,940 --> 00:35:41,380
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje mi molimo zajedno.

1022
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga, jako lijepo,

1023
00:35:45,239 --> 00:35:46,239
[SPEAKER_01] jako lijepo,

1024
00:35:46,239 --> 00:35:49,579
[SPEAKER_01] zazivam molitvu presvetog trojstva.

1025
00:35:49,579 --> 00:35:51,219
[SPEAKER_01] Otac, sin i dug sveti.

1026
00:35:51,219 --> 00:35:54,840
[SPEAKER_01] Predivne molitve gdje još jednom zazivamo trojstvo.

1027
00:35:55,260 --> 00:35:59,219
[SPEAKER_01] I onda na jednom trenutku svećinik polaže ruke.

1028
00:35:59,219 --> 00:36:00,639
[SPEAKER_01] Baš utišini.

1029
00:36:00,639 --> 00:36:01,679
[SPEAKER_01] Utišini.

1030
00:36:01,679 --> 00:36:04,480
[SPEAKER_01] Od svih polaganja ruke,

1031
00:36:04,480 --> 00:36:05,840
[SPEAKER_01] u svim sakramentima,

1032
00:36:05,840 --> 00:36:09,800
[SPEAKER_01] vjerujte mi da mi je ovo najdublje.

1033
00:36:09,800 --> 00:36:11,199
[SPEAKER_01] Baš utišini.

1034
00:36:11,199 --> 00:36:12,579
[SPEAKER_01] Samo utišini.

1035
00:36:13,099 --> 00:36:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] Polaže se ruke.

1036
00:36:14,059 --> 00:36:16,280
[SPEAKER_01] Jer svećiničke ruke su pomazane.

1037
00:36:16,280 --> 00:36:21,039
[SPEAKER_01] I svećinik kratko se zaustavi iznad glave i polaže ruke nad njim.

1038
00:36:21,039 --> 00:36:22,239
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno,

1039
00:36:22,239 --> 00:36:22,820
[SPEAKER_01] nakon toga,

1040
00:36:22,820 --> 00:36:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] vjernik ispruži svoje ruke.

1041
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] I ja ću pročitati formulu.

1042
00:36:27,619 --> 00:36:28,400
[SPEAKER_01] svećinik moli,

1043
00:36:28,400 --> 00:36:30,440
[SPEAKER_01] po ovome svetom pomazanju

1044
00:36:30,440 --> 00:36:32,320
[SPEAKER_01] i po svome preblago milosređu,

1045
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:34,679
[SPEAKER_01] nekada gospodin milošću duha svetoga pomogne.

1046
00:36:34,679 --> 00:36:38,019
[SPEAKER_01] I tada napravim križić sa posvećenim uljem na čelo.

1047
00:36:38,019 --> 00:36:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga,

1048
00:36:38,960 --> 00:36:41,219
[SPEAKER_01] nekada te oslobođena od grijeha spasi

1049
00:36:41,219 --> 00:36:42,699
[SPEAKER_01] i milostivo podigne.

1050
00:36:43,079 --> 00:36:44,480
[SPEAKER_01] I onda pomazujem ruke,

1051
00:36:44,480 --> 00:36:45,079
[SPEAKER_01] dlanove.

1052
00:36:45,079 --> 00:36:50,019
[SPEAKER_01] I što se tiče tog ulja,

1053
00:36:50,019 --> 00:36:52,400
[SPEAKER_01] to nije bilo koje ulje.

1054
00:36:52,400 --> 00:36:54,159
[SPEAKER_01] To je masino ulje

1055
00:36:54,159 --> 00:36:56,139
[SPEAKER_01] koje je posvetio nadbiskup.

1056
00:36:56,139 --> 00:36:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] Samo da vam malo približim nešto o tom ulju.

1057
00:36:58,739 --> 00:37:01,139
[SPEAKER_01] To nije ulje koje sam ja zvao

1058
00:37:01,139 --> 00:37:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] nekog moj prijeta na braću.

1059
00:37:02,619 --> 00:37:04,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ej, imaš ulje, aj pošaljim na bus.

1060
00:37:04,280 --> 00:37:06,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne.

1061
00:37:06,159 --> 00:37:08,559
[SPEAKER_01] Znate ko je to ulje?

1062
00:37:08,559 --> 00:37:11,380
[SPEAKER_01] Vrijedi ovo spominjan.

1063
00:37:12,119 --> 00:37:13,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam nikad radio masano ulje.

1064
00:37:13,619 --> 00:37:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] Ali navodno,

1065
00:37:15,699 --> 00:37:17,860
[SPEAKER_01] kad se radi to masano ulje,

1066
00:37:17,860 --> 00:37:20,239
[SPEAKER_01] ti stari kameni mlinovi,

1067
00:37:20,239 --> 00:37:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] sad ne znam kako oni to rade danas,

1068
00:37:21,820 --> 00:37:23,019
[SPEAKER_01] ali navodno onaj,

1069
00:37:23,019 --> 00:37:24,599
[SPEAKER_01] znate ono masne,

1070
00:37:24,599 --> 00:37:25,980
[SPEAKER_01] kad onaj kamen,

1071
00:37:25,980 --> 00:37:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] ona preša,

1072
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:28,920
[SPEAKER_01] zgniječi,

1073
00:37:28,920 --> 00:37:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] ono prvo ulje što iskoči,

1074
00:37:32,019 --> 00:37:32,539
[SPEAKER_01] ono pl.

1075
00:37:32,539 --> 00:37:34,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ej, to ulje se koristi.

1076
00:37:34,920 --> 00:37:36,480
[SPEAKER_01] Jer navodno,

1077
00:37:36,480 --> 00:37:38,219
[SPEAKER_01] oni više puta to ulje vraćaju,

1078
00:37:38,219 --> 00:37:39,719
[SPEAKER_01] pa masne, pa opet,

1079
00:37:39,719 --> 00:37:41,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa imaš drugu rundu, treću rundu.

1080
00:37:41,179 --> 00:37:42,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, prva runda ide sveći,

1081
00:37:42,880 --> 00:37:44,800
[SPEAKER_01] prva runda ide za sakrmet.

1082
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,340
[SPEAKER_01] Zamijeste vi to,

1083
00:37:46,340 --> 00:37:48,239
[SPEAKER_01] ono prvo što izađe.

1084
00:37:48,239 --> 00:37:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] To se pohrani

1085
00:37:51,440 --> 00:37:54,139
[SPEAKER_01] i na veliki četvrtak.

1086
00:37:54,139 --> 00:37:56,599
[SPEAKER_01] To je jedina misa u godinu

1087
00:37:56,599 --> 00:37:57,539
[SPEAKER_01] koja ima svoju temu.

1088
00:37:57,539 --> 00:37:59,460
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, svake nedelje imamo mise,

1089
00:37:59,460 --> 00:38:00,840
[SPEAKER_01] ali jedina misa

1090
00:38:00,840 --> 00:38:01,940
[SPEAKER_01] koja ima svoju temu,

1091
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:03,579
[SPEAKER_01] to je misa posveta ulja.

1092
00:38:03,659 --> 00:38:04,199
[SPEAKER_01] tako se zove.

1093
00:38:04,199 --> 00:38:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je veliki četvrtak ujtru,

1094
00:38:06,000 --> 00:38:07,460
[SPEAKER_01] uvijek u katedrali,

1095
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] ne bilo gdje,

1096
00:38:08,159 --> 00:38:09,159
[SPEAKER_01] nego u katedrali.

1097
00:38:09,159 --> 00:38:11,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ta misa je toliko svećana

1098
00:38:11,019 --> 00:38:12,320
[SPEAKER_01] da su sve druge mise

1099
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:14,519
[SPEAKER_01] dilijem nadbiskupije zabranjene.

1100
00:38:14,519 --> 00:38:16,179
[SPEAKER_01] Zato veliki četvrtak

1101
00:38:16,179 --> 00:38:17,000
[SPEAKER_01] nema jutarnje mise.

1102
00:38:18,000 --> 00:38:19,300
[SPEAKER_01] Svake godine ljudi kucu

1103
00:38:19,300 --> 00:38:20,360
[SPEAKER_01] E, otvaraj.

1104
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:22,679
[SPEAKER_01] Nema mise, zašto?

1105
00:38:22,679 --> 00:38:23,900
[SPEAKER_01] Velika četvrtak,

1106
00:38:23,900 --> 00:38:24,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa zato sam tu.

1107
00:38:24,860 --> 00:38:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Pa, onda ja moram njemu

1108
00:38:26,460 --> 00:38:27,699
[SPEAKER_01] cijelu teologiju objasniti.

1109
00:38:27,699 --> 00:38:30,219
[SPEAKER_01] Nema mise, veliki četvrtak,

1110
00:38:30,219 --> 00:38:30,659
[SPEAKER_01] nigdje,

1111
00:38:30,659 --> 00:38:32,659
[SPEAKER_01] samo u katedrali.

1112
00:38:32,659 --> 00:38:35,679
[SPEAKER_01] Svaki svećenik je dužan doć.

1113
00:38:35,679 --> 00:38:37,400
[SPEAKER_01] Čak ako ne dođeš,

1114
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:38,579
[SPEAKER_01] moraš se ispričati,

1115
00:38:38,579 --> 00:38:39,559
[SPEAKER_01] moraš imati razlog.

1116
00:38:39,559 --> 00:38:40,880
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim, ovo je ozbiljna stvar.

1117
00:38:40,880 --> 00:38:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] I na toj misi

1118
00:38:42,659 --> 00:38:44,400
[SPEAKER_01] nadbiskup,

1119
00:38:44,400 --> 00:38:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] ne neki svećenik,

1120
00:38:45,619 --> 00:38:46,659
[SPEAKER_01] neko nadbiskup

1121
00:38:46,659 --> 00:38:48,639
[SPEAKER_01] posvećuje to ulje.

1122
00:38:48,639 --> 00:38:51,139
[SPEAKER_01] Čime će se pomazivati

1123
00:38:51,139 --> 00:38:52,500
[SPEAKER_01] sve bolestnike tijekom godine.

1124
00:38:52,500 --> 00:38:53,619
[SPEAKER_01] I mi župnici,

1125
00:38:53,619 --> 00:38:54,000
[SPEAKER_01] odnosno,

1126
00:38:54,000 --> 00:38:54,380
[SPEAKER_01] kog godine,

1127
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:55,440
[SPEAKER_01] dad sam ja bio župnik,

1128
00:38:55,440 --> 00:38:56,900
[SPEAKER_01] dođeš i dobiješ

1129
00:38:56,900 --> 00:38:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] odmah nakon mise,

1130
00:38:58,159 --> 00:38:59,679
[SPEAKER_01] dobiješ svoju ampolicu

1131
00:38:59,679 --> 00:39:02,179
[SPEAKER_01] ulje za cijelu godinu.

1132
00:39:02,179 --> 00:39:04,519
[SPEAKER_01] Bolesničko i krizmaničko.

1133
00:39:04,519 --> 00:39:05,460
[SPEAKER_01] Ok?

1134
00:39:05,460 --> 00:39:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, braćo i seste,

1135
00:39:07,239 --> 00:39:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] to je to ulje.

1136
00:39:08,139 --> 00:39:10,340
[SPEAKER_01] To je to posvećeno ulje.

1137
00:39:10,340 --> 00:39:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] Koje sve je to ulje.

1138
00:39:12,460 --> 00:39:14,659
[SPEAKER_01] S time mi pomazujemo

1139
00:39:14,659 --> 00:39:15,980
[SPEAKER_01] naše vjernike.

1140
00:39:16,460 --> 00:39:18,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo nisam mislio govoriti,

1141
00:39:18,599 --> 00:39:20,760
[SPEAKER_01] ali smatrao sam važnim.

1142
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:21,519
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga,

1143
00:39:21,519 --> 00:39:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] molimo zajedno.

1144
00:39:22,699 --> 00:39:23,679
[SPEAKER_01] I tako,

1145
00:39:23,679 --> 00:39:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] sakrmenat je dovršen.

1146
00:39:25,420 --> 00:39:26,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ok.

1147
00:39:26,039 --> 00:39:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] Znate šta je meni puno važnije?

1148
00:39:28,619 --> 00:39:32,019
[SPEAKER_01] Učin si ovog sakrmenata.

1149
00:39:32,019 --> 00:39:33,699
[SPEAKER_01] Učin si.

1150
00:39:35,300 --> 00:39:36,380
[SPEAKER_01] ima nekoliko učinaka.

1151
00:39:36,380 --> 00:39:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ja moram priznat kao svećenik,

1152
00:39:39,260 --> 00:39:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] danas sam ja ostao paf.

1153
00:39:40,599 --> 00:39:41,019
[SPEAKER_01] Evo ga.

1154
00:39:41,019 --> 00:39:43,019
[SPEAKER_01] Ja, Bož mi,

1155
00:39:43,019 --> 00:39:44,260
[SPEAKER_01] nisam znao neke stvari.

1156
00:39:44,260 --> 00:39:45,239
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, ja sam danas

1157
00:39:45,239 --> 00:39:47,380
[SPEAKER_01] ovo iznova naučio.

1158
00:39:47,380 --> 00:39:49,300
[SPEAKER_01] Ne iznova prvi put.

1159
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] jesam ja prespavao to na KBF-u,

1160
00:39:52,920 --> 00:39:53,360
[SPEAKER_01] ne znam,

1161
00:39:53,360 --> 00:39:53,760
[SPEAKER_01] jesam,

1162
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:56,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali,

1163
00:39:56,739 --> 00:40:00,219
[SPEAKER_01] evo, jedva čekam da podijelim sakrmenat.

1164
00:40:00,219 --> 00:40:01,159
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, sljedeći puta.

1165
00:40:01,159 --> 00:40:02,719
[SPEAKER_01] Ne želim nikome bolest,

1166
00:40:02,719 --> 00:40:02,920
[SPEAKER_01] ali.

1167
00:40:05,579 --> 00:40:06,559
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, prvo.

1168
00:40:06,559 --> 00:40:08,159
[SPEAKER_01] Ovo su učinci.

1169
00:40:08,159 --> 00:40:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže,

1170
00:40:10,139 --> 00:40:12,519
[SPEAKER_01] osnovna milost ovog sakrmenata

1171
00:40:12,519 --> 00:40:13,699
[SPEAKER_01] je milost potpore,

1172
00:40:13,699 --> 00:40:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] mira i ohrabrenja.

1173
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] Za nadvladanje tegoba,

1174
00:40:17,559 --> 00:40:18,079
[SPEAKER_01] vlasti,

1175
00:40:18,079 --> 00:40:19,039
[SPEAKER_01] teškoj bolesti

1176
00:40:19,039 --> 00:40:20,619
[SPEAKER_01] ili staračkoj nemoći.

1177
00:40:20,619 --> 00:40:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] Danas mi pada naprijed

1178
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,039
[SPEAKER_01] ovoj prvo svjedočanstvo.

1179
00:40:25,039 --> 00:40:28,420
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam jednom podijelio

1180
00:40:28,420 --> 00:40:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] beličko poznajem mom tati.

1181
00:40:29,500 --> 00:40:31,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, to je bilo slučajno.

1182
00:40:31,619 --> 00:40:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] U smislu,

1183
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:35,300
[SPEAKER_01] imao sam pučke misije

1184
00:40:35,300 --> 00:40:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] u Kanadi,

1185
00:40:35,960 --> 00:40:36,639
[SPEAKER_01] u Misisagi,

1186
00:40:36,639 --> 00:40:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] župa Misisaga.

1187
00:40:37,539 --> 00:40:38,519
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno,

1188
00:40:38,519 --> 00:40:40,219
[SPEAKER_01] moji roditelji su dolazi svaku večer.

1189
00:40:40,219 --> 00:40:41,519
[SPEAKER_01] I župnik je tako zamislio.

1190
00:40:41,519 --> 00:40:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] Sedan dana sam bio za redu.

1191
00:40:42,860 --> 00:40:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] Jednu večer župnik je zamislio

1192
00:40:45,400 --> 00:40:47,199
[SPEAKER_01] pokorničko i bleško pomezanje.

1193
00:40:47,199 --> 00:40:49,500
[SPEAKER_01] I mi smo imali taj uvodni obred

1194
00:40:49,500 --> 00:40:50,159
[SPEAKER_01] i tako dalje.

1195
00:40:50,159 --> 00:40:51,000
[SPEAKER_01] I najavljeno,

1196
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:52,320
[SPEAKER_01] bolesnici i starsi došli.

1197
00:40:52,320 --> 00:40:54,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ja uopće nisam razmišljao.

1198
00:40:54,260 --> 00:40:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ja gledam u redu,

1199
00:40:55,340 --> 00:40:56,159
[SPEAKER_01] moj tata stoji.

1200
00:40:56,159 --> 00:40:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo mi je malo neugodno.

1201
00:40:58,980 --> 00:40:59,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam htio da moj tata...

1202
00:40:59,920 --> 00:41:00,219
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

1203
00:41:00,599 --> 00:41:02,659
[SPEAKER_01] jednom mi je brat došao za ispred

1204
00:41:02,659 --> 00:41:03,340
[SPEAKER_01] i ja sam ga potiruo.

1205
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:05,940
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

1206
00:41:05,940 --> 00:41:08,380
[SPEAKER_01] prvo nisam znao kako ću reagirati.

1207
00:41:08,380 --> 00:41:09,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ja nisam znao

1208
00:41:09,500 --> 00:41:11,539
[SPEAKER_01] oče to mene ganuti.

1209
00:41:11,539 --> 00:41:13,800
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam baš u tom trenutku

1210
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] htio neke emocije pokazati.

1211
00:41:15,500 --> 00:41:16,139
[SPEAKER_01] Mislim,

1212
00:41:16,139 --> 00:41:18,219
[SPEAKER_01] stoji predamnom čovjek

1213
00:41:18,219 --> 00:41:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] koji je moj tata,

1214
00:41:19,059 --> 00:41:22,619
[SPEAKER_01] čije tijelo slabi,

1215
00:41:22,619 --> 00:41:25,239
[SPEAKER_01] koji je krh i slab,

1216
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,239
[SPEAKER_01] a on je za mene

1217
00:41:26,239 --> 00:41:27,659
[SPEAKER_01] simbol autoriteta

1218
00:41:27,659 --> 00:41:28,940
[SPEAKER_01] i muževnost

1219
00:41:28,940 --> 00:41:29,519
[SPEAKER_01] i muškost

1220
00:41:29,519 --> 00:41:30,059
[SPEAKER_01] i sve to

1221
00:41:30,059 --> 00:41:32,260
[SPEAKER_01] i on stoji predamnom.

1222
00:41:32,260 --> 00:41:35,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam ga pomozao

1223
00:41:35,059 --> 00:41:36,699
[SPEAKER_01] i ništa.

1224
00:41:36,699 --> 00:41:37,539
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo dalje.

1225
00:41:37,539 --> 00:41:39,539
[SPEAKER_01] I sutradan,

1226
00:41:39,539 --> 00:41:41,280
[SPEAKER_01] kad smo bili sami,

1227
